dians that believes in consumerism. To them issues like patriotism and giving ones life for ones beliefs is the stuff stuffy text- books are made of. They would rather party than be patriots.<p>In the film both the 1930s British India and the India Today run parallel and intersect with each other at crucial points. As the film reaches its resolution the line between past and present blurs, as they become one in spirit.<p>The film changed the face of how youth looks at their rights, their duties and what rebel means to them!',12.99,8.82,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51k1HsK3d7L._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:54:39','2011-12-16 06:54:39',0),(10,5,'http://www.amazon.com/Dil-chahta-hai-Amir-Khan/dp/B0016GOM0Q%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0016GOM0Q','Dil chahta hai',NULL,8.79,5.89,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51WCCbFBl9L._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:54:41','2011-12-16 06:54:41',0),(11,5,'http://www.amazon.com/Sholay-Bollywood-DVD-Amitabh-Bachchan/dp/B00008N72N%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00008N72N','Sholay Bollywood DVD',NULL,9.98,6.69,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51DVNAD0BDL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:54:44','2011-12-16 06:54:44',0),(12,5,'http://www.amazon.com/Swades-People-Blu-ray-Shahrukh-Khan/dp/B003ZZK2NW%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB003ZZK2NW','Swades We the People [Blu-ray]','Original UTV Motion Pictures Blu-ray Disc',36.98,17.29,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51s6qkYMt4L._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:54:45','2011-12-16 06:54:45',0),(13,9,'http://www.amazon.com/Potter-Deathly-Hallows-UltraViolet-Digital/dp/B001UV4XIS%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001UV4XIS','Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows, Part 2 (+ UltraViolet Digital Copy)','In the epic finale, the battle between the good and evil forces of the wizarding world escalates into an all-out war. The stakes have never been higher and no one is safe. But it is Harry who may be called upon to make the ultimate sacrifice as he draws closer to the climactic showdown with Lord Voldemort. It all ends here. ',28.98,9.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/514zkTMnQrL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:54:49','2011-12-16 06:54:49',0),(14,5,'http://www.amazon.com/Tarzan-Special-Tony-Goldwyn/dp/B000AAF1TU%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB000AAF1TU','Tarzan (Special Edition)','Swing into action and adventure with Disney\'s original classic, TARZAN(R), packed with fun-filled bonus features and award-winning music such as the memorable \"You\'ll Be In My Heart\" and \"Trashin\' The Camp.\" Disney\'s magnificent animated adaptation of Edgar Rice Burrough\'s story of the ape man begins deep within the jungle when baby Tarzan is adopted by a family of gorillas. Even though he is shunned as a \"hairless wonder\" by their leader, Tarzan is accepted by the gorillas and raised as one of their own. Together with his wisecracking ape buddy Terk and neurotic elephant pal Tantor, Tarzan learns how to \"surf\" and swing through the trees and survive in the animal kingdom. His \"Two Worlds\" collide with the arrival of humans, forcing Tarzan to choose between a \"civilized\" life with the beautiful Jane and the life he knows and loves with his gorilla family. Filled with humor, heart, and hilarious fun, TARZAN is an unforgettable adventure you\'ll watch again and again.~~TARZAN(R) Owned by Edgar Rice Burroughs, Inc. And Used by Permission. TARZAN (C) Edgar Rice Burroughs, Inc. and Disney Enterprises, Inc. All Rights Reserved.',19.99,14.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/image