 and mouse, with a villain whose identity is far too predictable. With no dramatic buildup and several superfluous characters to distract its focus, the film\'s momentum plays out like a rote exercise compared to the high stakes of the earlier film. <i>--Jeff Shannon</i>',9.98,1.5,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51JRJ8M8FWL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:59:08','2011-12-16 06:59:08',0),(89,28,'http://www.amazon.com/Forbidden-Kingdom-Jet-Li/dp/B001BEK8HO%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001BEK8HO','The Forbidden Kingdom','Individually, they\'ve starred in the most adrenaline-pumping martial-arts adventures ever.  Together for the first time, Jet Li and Jackie Chan join forces to create the greates epic of them all- THE FORBIDDEN KINGDOM.  As ancient Chinese warriors, they must train and mentor a 21st century kung-fu fanatic who\'s been summoned to fight a centuries-old battle and free the imprisoned Monkey King.  If you\'re a fighting fan, the wait is over.  The team is ready.  The Kingdom has arrived.',14.98,9.49,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41oUJ-vzXvL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:59:11','2011-12-16 06:59:11',0),(90,28,'http://www.amazon.com/Potter-Deathly-Hallows-UltraViolet-Digital/dp/B001UV4XIS%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001UV4XIS','Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows, Part 2 (+ UltraViolet Digital Copy)','In the epic finale, the battle between the good and evil forces of the wizarding world escalates into an all-out war. The stakes have never been higher and no one is safe. But it is Harry who may be called upon to make the ultimate sacrifice as he draws closer to the climactic showdown with Lord Voldemort. It all ends here. ',28.98,9.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/514zkTMnQrL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:59:14','2011-12-16 06:59:14',0),(9