tive%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB004EKOP80','Golmaal 3 Bollywood DVD With English Subtitles','Madhav (Warsi), Laxman (Khemu) and Lucky (Kapoor) are the three scheming sons of Pritam (Mithun) who manage to lure Vasooli (Mukesh Tiwari) into one scheme after another. They find competition from three other down-on-their-luck kids Gopal (Ajay Devgn), Laxman (Shreyas Talapade) and Dabbu (Kareena Kapoor) with funding from Puppy bhai (Johnny Lever). Gopal and Laxman are the sons of Geeta (Ratna Pathak Shah). They end up destroying each others businesses. What the two groups don t know is that their parents are unrequited ex-lovers. When Dabbu finds out she schemes and unites the two lovers in a marriage without letting their children know about their step-brothers. All hell breaks loose when they finally find out and a hilarious war engulfs between the two groups right under their parents noses.',19.98,10.5,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61Uu-ji8zwL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 07:02:56','2011-12-16 07:02:56',0),(148,63,'http://www.amazon.com/Evil-Dead-Blu-ray-Bruce-Campbell/dp/B003IY48PS%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB003IY48PS','The Evil Dead [Blu-ray]','The Evil Dead, director Sam Raimi\'s (Darkman, Quick & The Dead, Army Of Darkness) first feature film, is a true cult classic in every sense of the word. Originally released in 1982, The Evil Dead tells the tale of a group of friends who go to a cabin in the woods, where they find an unspeakable evil lurking in the forest. They find the Necronomicon, the Book Of The Dead, and the taped translation of the text. Once the tape is played, the evil is released. One by one, the teens become deadly zombies. With only one remaining (Bruce Campbell), it is up to him to survive the night and battle The Evil Dead.',29.97,10.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51FkMy%2BXo5L._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 07:03:03','2011-12-16 07:03: