INSERT INTO `amazon_musics` VALUES (5,5,'http://www.amazon.com/Most-Relaxing-Classical-Music-Universe/dp/B00008RH16%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00008RH16','The Most Relaxing Classical Music in the Universe',NULL,11.98,7.98,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41B97ECM7ML._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:17','2011-12-16 06:47:17',0),(6,5,'http://www.amazon.com/Ultimate-Hits-Rock-Never-Forgets/dp/B0043URV5U%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0043URV5U','Ultimate Hits: Rock And Roll Never Forgets','2011 two CD compilation from the Rock singer, songwriter and icon. For the first time, all of Bob Seger\'s top hits have been gathered for a career-spanning double disc set. The 26-track collection includes \"Night Moves,\" \"Turn The Page,\" \"Hollywood Nights,\" \"Mainstreet,\" \"Old Time Rock And Roll,\" \"Like A Rock,\" \"Her Strut,\" \"We\'ve Got Tonight,\" \"Against The Wind,\" \"Still The Same,\" and many other classics, as well as the Detroit rocker\'s two #1 radio singles from this year, \"Downtown Train\" and his current #1 Classic Rock hit, \"Hey Hey Hey Hey (Going Back To Birmingham).\" All songs on the album have been meticulously remastered from the original master tapes, including the original mono version of Seger\'s first hit \"Ramblin\' Gamblin\' Man\" and Seger\'s timeless rendition of the holiday classic \"Little Drummer Boy.\"',19.98,11.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51KeP3LcJML._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:20','2011-12-16 06:47:20',0),(7,8,'http://www.amazon.com/Enrique-Iglesias/dp/B0000658G9%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0000658G9','Enrique Iglesias','Light rock tunes and soft pop ballads marked Enrique Iglesias\'s 1995 debut, but what obviously propelled him to the top of the charts was his young good looks and his pedigree, son of perhaps the most famous troubadour in the music world--Julio Iglesias. \"Trapecista\" and \"Experiencia Religiosa\" were solid tunes with catchy hooks. And even on the simple tune \"Por Amarte,\" one can detect Iglesias exploring wailful tones and learning the power of melodic phrasing. In \"Si Tu Te Vas,\" he examines idealistic love, while \"Inalcansable\" captures youthful dreams. Those songs are the bright spots in an otherwise pedestrian pop-ballad CD. The fact that Iglesias scored five consecutive number one singles on Billboard from this CD may attest more to the power of the elder Iglesias\'s worldwide fans. <I>--Ramiro Burr</I>',5.98,6.15,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51VybgmaCCL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:23','2011-12-16 06:47:23',0),(8,13,'http://www.amazon.com/Sing-Bruno-Mars-Karaoke-CDG/dp/B0058DXRHC%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0058DXRHC','Sing Bruno Mars (Karaoke CDG)','In October 2010, Bruno Mars released his debut album, Doo-Wops & Hooligans. Anchored by the worldwide number one singles <i>Just the Way You Are</i> and <i>Grenade</i>, the album peaked at number three on the Billboard 200. Mars was nominated for seven Grammys at the 53rd Grammy Awards, winning Best Male Pop Vocal Performance for <i>Just the Way You Are</i>. Sing nine hits in the style of this popular new recording artist, presented in their original keys and tempo. For each song, the 2 CDs include a complete version, a version with backup vocals, as well as an instrumental-only track.',19.95,15.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51k5-8pdkhL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:26','2011-12-16 06:47:26',0),(9,13,'http://www.amazon.com/Lil-Wayne-No-Ceilings-Waybe/dp/B001RLD6DY%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001RLD6DY','Lil Wayne - No Ceilings','We\'re talking the old mixed with the new -- & all the classic street and underground Cash Money Records & Young Money Entertainment\'s classics and the movies altogether in one place w/ bonus outtakes and never-before-seen clips off of the, \"The Carter\" behind-the-scenes footage & all-access pass to things you didn\'t see with the \"The Carter\" movie. This DVD features: Lil Wayne, Birdman, Slim, Nicki Minaj, Mack Maine, Lil Chuckee, Drake, Gudda Gudda, Tyga, T-Streets, Jae Millz, Ceelow, Jay Sean, Models, Directors & More. The modern day Cash Money machine is displayed here as HoodPromoTV touches down with a look at the empire: \"No Celings\" the DVD. This Video Anthology is mixed with Soundtrack, Behind the scenes of the music videos, Videos, Live Performances, Interviews & Freestyles, which documents the life of Lil\' Wayne and the rich & famous lifestyles of the CMB/YME Artist. This DVD also includes never-before-seen Lil\' Wayne behind the scenes music videos including \"Bedrock\" and \"Cash Money Heroes\" and More Weezy later checks in with exclusive \"Carter III\" live performances of \"A Mille\" in front of a sold out arena, as he gives a performance of a lifetime for all those in attendance. ALSO FEATURED IN THIS DVD: Baby in London w/CMB & YME, Weed Perscription, Jay Sean speaks on joining the cash money family, FREESTYLE w/Mack Maine @ Jimmy Kimmel, and meet the newest members of Young Money & the rest of the Cash Money family!',14.95,14.95,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51%2BinZs4GVL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:28','2011-12-16 06:47:28',0),(10,13,'http://www.amazon.com/U2-360%C2%B0-ROSE-BOWL-Digipack/dp/B003ELOQCK%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB003ELOQCK','U2 - 360° AT THE ROSE BOWL [2 DVD Digipack]','<b>U2\'S RECORD BREAKING ROSE BOWL CONCERT</b><BR>  Filmed on 25th October 2009<BR>    <P>U2360° At The Rose Bowl was the penultimate gig of last year\'s U2360° tour in support of their Grammy-nominated album No Line on The Horizon. The Rose Bowl performance was the band\'s biggest show of 2009 and U2\'s biggest ever US show, with a live audience in excess of 97,000.  The show was also streamed across seven continents via YouTube. The first ever live streaming of a full-length stadium concert, U2360° at the Rose Bowl had over 10 million views on the channel in one week.     <P>Shot entirely in HD, the concert was filmed with 27 cameras and directed by Tom Krueger who had previously worked on U23D, the first live action 3D concert movie taken from U2\'s Vertigo Tour.  Available in standard and two disc deluxe DVD formats, U2360° At The Rose Bowl will also be U2\'s first concert available in Blu-ray. The deluxe formats and the Blu-ray will feature a new documentary called Squaring the Circle: Creating U2360°, with new interviews from U2, Paul McGuinness and the team behind the touring production.<BR>    ',29.98,19.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/510EdYwIhzL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:35','2011-12-16 06:47:35',0),(11,13,'http://www.amazon.com/Shallow-Bay-Best-Breaking-Benjamin/dp/B0055CAIJQ%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0055CAIJQ','Shallow Bay: The Best of Breaking Benjamin','Deluxe edition includes a bonus CD containing nine additional tracks including remixes and rarities. 2011 collection from the twice-platinum Alt-Rock outfit.  Shallow Bay: The Best of Breaking Benjamin compiles the hit songs that have taken Breaking Benjamin to the upper echelon of today\'s modern rock bands. Including the breakthrough smash \"So Cold\" and continuing up to the band\'s latest success with \"Give Me A Sign\", the record represents songs from every facet of the band\'s career as well as including the most recent hit song, a remix of the live favorite, \"Blow Me Away\".',19.99,12.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51Cg7ZmFckL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:38','2011-12-16 06:47:38',0),(12,13,'http://www.amazon.com/Avril-Lavigne-Best-Damn-Toronto/dp/B001AQURBA%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001AQURBA','Avril Lavigne: The Best Damn Tour - Live In Toronto','Explicit Version. 2008 DVD Best Damn Tour of Avril Lavigne Live In Toronto!  Pop-punk princess Avril Lavigne plays the hits that earned her legions of screaming fans (and launched a thousand ringtones) on The Best Damn Tour,  a full-length presentation of her 2008 concert in Toronto. Opening with monster hit \"Girlfriend,\" Lavigne rocks through every one of her major singles, including \"Complicated,\" \"My Happy Ending,\" and the ubiquitous \"Sk8R BOI.\"',16.98,14.69,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51XIT%2BSv-tL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:40','2011-12-16 06:47:40',0),(13,13,'http://www.amazon.com/Justin-Timberlake-Justified-Videos/dp/B0000C7PWC%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0000C7PWC','Justin Timberlake - Justified: The Videos','JUSTIFIED: THE VIDEOS - DVD Movie',11.98,9.99,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41r3i9s-YnL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:42','2011-12-16 06:47:42',0),(14,13,'http://www.amazon.com/50-Cent-Future/dp/B000J103L6%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB000J103L6','50 Cent Is the Future',NULL,9.99,10.02,'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51WcGbqdEgL._SL160_.jpg','2011-12-16 06:47:45','2011-12-16 06:47:45',0),(15,13,'http://www.amazon.com/Kailasa-%7E-Kailash-Kher/dp/B001P9O8V2%3FSubscriptionId%3D0BPKS2SXV4J9CRB2GVR2%26tag%3Dcalibanorg-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001P9O8V2','Kailasa ~ 